        We collect third party personally identifiable information on our site. When a user creates an account, they have the option to add contacts to their account. This information is not used for any promotional purposes by Litigo.co. We use this information to provide the communication services requested by the user [such as sending out invoices or other email communications the user may execute in their account.] We do not share this information with any third parties for their promotional purposes.<br>
